sub_title: CEO at Inter IKEA Group | IKEA
summary:
IKEA is in my heart, and I strongly believe in our vision to create a better everyday life for the many. So it’s my amazing privilege to lead Inter IKEA Group (Inter IKEA Group includes the IKEA franchisor, range, supply and some industrial activities). 
 
I’m passionate about transforming business and people for the better. That means making great products and services available for as many people as possible. And it means keeping things simple even as you scale a global brand. Most of all, it means working together towards a shared and common goal. 
 
My IKEA career started more than 20 years ago, but since then I’ve also lead other retail businesses as CEO. My most recent role was managing director of Inter IKEA Systems, the IKEA franchisor.
 
In all my roles, I’ve learned that the success of any organisation lies in leading business through people. I’m proud to work together with all 12 IKEA franchisees and more than 200,000 IKEA co-workers around the world to bring our vision to life.
